_sText:
Poolparty with better graphics, additional and less edgy cover, actual
pool water, particle streams, color correction and atmosphere.

Feature List:
* Water particles streaming out of the walls
* Animated water refraction on ceiling
* Pool water
* Ambient sounds for burbling water
* Color Correction
* Atmosphaerical reverb soundscapes
* Setting defining areas behind each spawn
* Easteregg song from Prince of Persia 4.


Easter egg song: "Time only Knows" by Chatwood

[Poolbase Preview on Youtube.com]

Have fun!
